@startuml
autoactivate on 
participant "App" as  App
participant Board
participant USBStream
participant "FlashManager" as FM 
participant "BootloaderCom" as BC


App -> Board: Process
Board --> App
Board -> USBStream: Process
USBStream--> Board

alt if(Idle) 
App -> BC: Process
BC -> FM: sendcommand()
FM -> USBStream: write()
USBStream --> FM: writtenbytes
FM --> BC: true
BC --> App
end alt

alt if (waitingforResponse)
App -> BC: Process

BC -> FM: readResponse()
FM -> USBStream: read
USBStream --> FM: 
BC -> FM : isComplete()
FM --> BC: true
BC-> BC: checkresponse()
BC -> FM: set Idle
BC --> App: true
end alt

@enduml
